@startuml
title E2E 시나리오: LIN Fault Detection → CAN Routing → UDS Diagnostics → OTA Update

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam shadowing false

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor White
    BorderColor Black
    FontSize 12
    FontStyle bold
}

skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor Black
    LifeLineBorderColor Gray
    GroupBorderColor DimGray
    GroupBackgroundColor #F5F5F5
    DividerBorderColor DimGray
    DividerBackgroundColor #EEEEEE
}

' ─── Participants ─────────────────────────────────────────────
participant "WindowMotorECU\n<color:DarkOrange>(LIN Slave 0x21)</color>" as WM   #NavajoWhite
participant "DoorModule FL~RR\n<color:DarkOrange>(LIN Slave 0x22~0x25)</color>" as DOOR #NavajoWhite
participant "BCM\n<color:DarkBlue>(LIN Master)</color>"                          as BCM  #LightYellow
participant "Gateway\n<color:DimGray>(CGW)</color>"                              as GW   #LightGray
participant "Cluster\n<color:FireBrick>(HMI)</color>"                           as CLU  #MistyRose
participant "Tester\n<color:DarkGreen>(CANoe)</color>"                          as TEST #LightCyan
participant "OTA Server\n<color:DarkGreen>(DoIP)</color>"                       as OTA  #LightCyan

' ─── Phase 0: LIN 정상 동작 ────────────────────────────────────
== <color:DimGray>Phase 0: LIN 정상 동작 (Normal Operation)</color> ==

note over WM, BCM #NavajoWhite
  LIN 2.2A, 19.2 kbps
  WindowMotorECU: 10ms 주기 전송
  DoorModule ×4:  50ms 주기 전송
end note

loop LIN 정상 주기 (Normal)
    WM   -> BCM : <color:DarkOrange>LIN 0x21</color> — Motor_Current=10A\nMotor_Status=RUNNING, Motor_Direction=UP
    DOOR -> BCM : <color:DarkOrange>LIN 0x22~0x25</color> — Door_Position=CLOSED\nLock_Status=LOCKED, Window_Position=50%
end

note over BCM : Motor_Current ≤ 50A → 정상 (DTC 없음)

' ─── Phase 1: Fault Detection ──────────────────────────────────
== <color:FireBrick>Phase 1: 고장 감지 및 경고등 점등 (Fault Detection)</color> ==

note right of WM #LightSalmon
  **[Fault Injection]**
  Panel SysVar:
  LIN::motorCurrent = 55A
end note

WM -> WM : LIN::motorCurrent 갱신\n(gMotorCurrent = 55.0A)

WM -> BCM : <color:DarkOrange>LIN 0x21</color> (10ms)\n[Motor_Current = 55A, Motor_Status=RUNNING]
activate BCM #LightYellow

    BCM -> BCM : Motor_Current(55A) > Threshold(50A)\n→ 과전류 감지!\n→ DTC B1234 생성 (gFaultActive=1, gDTC_Code=0xB234)

    BCM -> WM : <color:DarkOrange>LIN Control</color> — Motor_Stop 명령

    BCM -> GW : <color:Purple>CAN-LS 0x500</color> (10ms)\nBCM_FaultStatus [WindowMotorOvercurrent=1, DTC=0xB234]
    activate GW #LightGray
        GW -> CLU : <color:Red>CAN-HS 0x500</color> (Routed ≤5ms)\nBCM_FaultStatus [WindowMotorOvercurrent=1]
        activate CLU #MistyRose
            CLU -> CLU : WARNING_TYPE=OVERCURRENT\n→ <color:FireBrick>RED 경고등 점등</color> (FTTI < 50ms)
        deactivate CLU
    deactivate GW

deactivate BCM

note over BCM #LightSalmon
  DTC U0100 감시:
  LIN 프레임 미수신 >50ms → LIN 통신 이상 DTC 추가 생성
end note

' ─── Phase 2: UDS Diagnostics ──────────────────────────────────
== <color:DarkGoldenRod>Phase 2: UDS 진단 및 DTC 처리 (Diagnostics)</color> ==

TEST -> GW : <color:Purple>CAN-LS 0x7DF</color> — UDS 0x10 0x03\n(Extended Diagnostic Session)
activate GW #LightGray
    GW -> BCM : Forward
    activate BCM #LightYellow
        BCM --> GW : Response 0x50 0x03 (Positive)
    deactivate BCM
    GW --> TEST : Forward
deactivate GW

TEST -> GW : <color:Purple>CAN-LS 0x7DF</color> — UDS 0x19 0x02\n(Read DTC by Status Mask)
activate GW #LightGray
    GW -> BCM : Forward
    activate BCM #LightYellow
        BCM --> GW : Response 0x59 — DTC B1234 Active\n(Status=0x08, Confirmed & Failed)
    deactivate BCM
    GW --> TEST : Forward
deactivate GW

note right of TEST : DTC B1234 수신 확인 ✓

TEST -> GW : <color:Purple>CAN-LS 0x7DF</color> — UDS 0x14\n(Clear Diagnostic Information)
activate GW #LightGray
    GW -> BCM : Forward
    activate BCM #LightYellow
        BCM -> BCM : DTC B1234 삭제\ngFaultActive = 0, gDTC_Code = 0x0000

        BCM -> GW : <color:Purple>CAN-LS 0x500</color>\nBCM_FaultStatus [WindowMotorOvercurrent=0]
        activate GW #LightGray
            GW -> CLU : <color:Red>CAN-HS 0x500</color> (Routed)\n[WindowMotorOvercurrent=0]
            activate CLU #MistyRose
                CLU -> CLU : WarnLampRed = 0\n<color:DimGray>경고등 소등</color>
            deactivate CLU
        deactivate GW

        BCM --> GW : Response 0x54 (Positive — DTC Cleared)
    deactivate BCM
    GW --> TEST : Forward
deactivate GW

' ─── Phase 3: OTA Update ───────────────────────────────────────
== <color:DarkGreen>Phase 3: OTA 펌웨어 업데이트 (OTA Update)</color> ==

OTA -> GW : <color:Blue>Ethernet/DoIP</color> — Routing Activation (0xE001)
activate GW #LightGray
    GW -> GW  : DoIP 세션 확립 (192.168.1.100 ↔ 192.168.1.10)
    GW --> OTA : Response 0xE001 (Success)
deactivate GW

OTA -> GW : <color:Blue>DoIP</color> — UDS 0x10 0x02\n(Programming Session)
activate GW #LightGray
    GW -> BCM : Forward (DoIP → CAN-LS Bridge)
    activate BCM #LightYellow
        BCM --> GW : Response 0x50 0x02
    deactivate BCM
    GW --> OTA : Forward (CAN-LS → DoIP Bridge)
deactivate GW

OTA -> GW : <color:Blue>DoIP</color> — UDS 0x34\n(Request Download — memoryAddress, memorySize)
activate GW #LightGray
    GW -> BCM : Forward
    activate BCM #LightYellow
        BCM --> GW : Response 0x74 (MaxBlockLength = 0x0400)
    deactivate BCM
    GW --> OTA : Forward
deactivate GW

loop 펌웨어 전송 (N Blocks, 각 1KB)
    OTA -> GW : <color:Blue>DoIP</color> — UDS 0x36 (Transfer Data, BlockSequence++)
    activate GW #LightGray
        GW -> BCM : Forward
        activate BCM #LightYellow
            BCM --> GW : Response 0x76 (Positive)
        deactivate BCM
        GW --> OTA : Forward
    deactivate GW
end

OTA -> GW : <color:Blue>DoIP</color> — UDS 0x37\n(Request Transfer Exit)
activate GW #LightGray
    GW -> BCM : Forward
    activate BCM #LightYellow
        BCM -> BCM : CRC-32 검증\n→ 일치: Flash 완료, BCM 재시작
        BCM --> GW : Response 0x77 (Positive — Transfer Complete)
    deactivate BCM
    GW --> OTA : Forward
deactivate GW

note over WM, OTA #LightGreen
  **[검증 완료]**
  BCM 재시작 후 LIN Slave 재동작 확인
  DTC B1234 소거 상태 유지
  Cluster 경고등 소등 상태 유지
end note

@enduml
